Perlindungan.

1154
01:53:15.295 --> 01:53:17.422
Ayo!

1155
01:53:29.017 --> 01:53:30.727
Cepat, kulit putih!

1156
01:53:35.773 --> 01:53:37.358
Sebelah sini.

1157
01:53:38.401 --> 01:53:40.153
Sisi ini, Goody.

1158
01:53:41.612 --> 01:53:44.157
Ayo, Faraday!

1159
01:53:46.534 --> 01:53:48.286
Apa ini?

1160
01:54:03.342 --> 01:54:04.969
Tembak dua orang di belakang.

1161
01:54:07.596 --> 01:54:09.098
Tembak menara gereja.

1162
01:54:18.023 --> 01:54:19.817
Aku mengenai dia!

1163
01:54:35.624 --> 01:54:37.459
Goody.

1164
01:55:46.986 --> 01:55:48.612
Kemari, Nak!

1165
01:56:01.124 --> 01:56:02.960
Tetap di bawah, Nak.

1166
01:56:53.092 --> 01:56:54.802
Ayo pergi.

1167
01:56:57.763 --> 01:56:59.599
- Dinamit.
- Aku selalu beruntung...


1168
01:56:59.682 --> 01:57:01.809
Dengan orang bermata satu.

1169
01:57:59.908 --> 01:58:02.243
<i>Bawa mereka masuk</i>

1170
01:59:09.601 --> 01:59:11.645
Chisolm?

1171
01:59:12.896 --> 01:59:15.148
Perlukah aku tahu nama itu?

