1202
02:02:33.218 --> 02:02:35.345
Yang mereka gantung.

1203
02:02:35.429 --> 02:02:39.432
Apa mereka berdoa saat kau
menaruh tali di leherku saat itu?


1204
02:02:41.309 --> 02:02:43.270
Berdoalah.

1205
02:02:43.353 --> 02:02:46.648
Aku ingat. Chisolm.

1206
02:02:46.731 --> 02:02:50.151
